---
import UmaLayout from "@/layouts/UmaLayout.astro";
import Music from "../../components/widget/Music.astro";

const title = "TM Opera O";
const cardname = "O Sole So";
const date = "07-28-2025";
const rank = "★★★";
const racetype = "turf, med, long";
const strat = "pace, late";
const potential = "4";
const cardimg =
    "https://gametora.com/images/umamusume/characters/chara_stand_1015_101501.png";
---

<UmaLayout
    title={title}
    ,
    cardname={cardname}
    ,
    date={date}
    ,
    rank={rank}
    ,
    racetype={racetype}
    ,
    strat={strat}
    ,
    potential={potential}
    ,
    cardimg={cardimg}
>
    <div slot="box-left">
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>trait</th>
                <th>base</th>
                <th>bonus</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Speed</td>
                <td>75</td>
                <td></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Stam</td>
                <td>108</td>
                <td>20%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Power</td>
                <td>75</td>
                <td></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Guts</td>
                <td>102</td>
                <td></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wit</td>
                <td>90</td>
                <td>10%</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <button type="button" class="collapsible">skills</button>
        <div class="colcontent">
            <h3>skills</h3>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>skill</th>
                    <th>name</th>
                    <th>conditions</th>
                    <th>effect</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td
                        ><img
                            src="https://gametora.com/images/umamusume/skill_icons/utx_ico_skill_20013.png"
                        /></td
                    >
                    <td>This Dance Is for Vittoria!</td>
                    <td
                        >If uma 1 horse length or less behind or infront, in 4th
                        place or higher, and on or beyond the last corner</td
                    >
                    <td>Increase target speed 35% for 5 sec</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td
                        ><img
                            src="https://gametora.com/images/umamusume/skill_icons/utx_ico_skill_20012.png"
                        /></td
                    >
                    <td>Speed Star</td>
                    <td
                        >If pace chaser, pass wit check, on final corner, and in
                        first half of the pack
                    </td>
                    <td>Increase target speed 35% for 1.2 sec</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td
                        ><img
                            src="https://gametora.com/images/umamusume/skill_icons/utx_ico_skill_20011.png"
                        /></td
                    >
                    <td>Up Tempo</td>
                    <td
                        >If medium distance, first half of the pack, pass wit
                        and mid race
                    </td>
                    <td>Increase target speed 15% for .9 sec</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td
                        ><img
                            src="https://gametora.com/images/umamusume/skill_icons/utx_ico_skill_10021.png"
                        /></td
                    >
                    <td>Non-Standard Distance</td>
                    <td>If distance is not divisble by 400 </td>
                    <td>Stamina up 40-60</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td
                        ><img
                            src="https://gametora.com/images/umamusume/skill_icons/utx_ico_skill_20011.png"
                        /></td
                    >
                    <td>Straightaway Adept</td>
                    <td>If wit check passed and on random straight </td>
                    <td>Increase target speed 15% for 0.9 sec</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div slot="box-right">
        <h3>URA Build</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>Goal stats:</b> - 900-1100 speed, 800-900 stam, 500-700 power,
                400 guts, 400 wit
            </li>
            <li><b>Support Recs:</b>2-3 stamina, 3-4 speed</li>
            <div class="small">
                <img
                    src="https://img.game8.co/4216916/3c352856b5348f43d8c4f057c6a40b84.png/show"
                />
                <img
                    src="https://img.game8.co/4218616/5381cc866a49ad65f83876f47662001e.png/show"
                />
                <img
                    src="https://img.game8.co/4217015/153838608e154b6d9fc4f2739cab45c7.png/show"
                />
                <img
                    src="https://img.game8.co/4216926/2bc1f9e84ecbf9679cdd487ffeaf9e26.png/show"
                />
                <img
                    src="https://img.game8.co/4216919/54fb7e8c2ee829ca0d4ec498ca151171.png/show"
                />
                <img
                    src="https://img.game8.co/4216928/014824fcd1d9de631eccb6a433409cee.png/show"
                />
                <img
                    src="https://img.game8.co/4216967/4f3a2e381dc8d111a93fe38c85ad99af.png/show"
                />
                <img
                    src="https://j-img.game8.co/5999066/86be0ae4e735c6322c615dcdcb854e58.png/show"
                />
            </div>
            <li>
                <b>Parents:</b> Mejiro McQueen (high combatibility), Narita Brian
                (high combatibility), Daiwa Scarlet (Race Planner skill), Oguri Cap
                (unique skill good for pace strategy)
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>legacy sparks:</b>9★ stamina, 9★ power, 3★ chaser, 3★ medium
                3★ long
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Skills:</b><ul>
                    <li>Speed star/prepared to pass (innate)</li>
                    <li>Race Planner/preffered position</li>
                    <li>Gourmand/Hydrate (Spe card)</li>
                    <li>Swinging Maestro/Corner Recovery (Creek Card)</li>
                    <li>Home stretch haste (SC or SW card)</li>
                    <li>Ramp Up/It's On</li>
                    <li></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Misc:</b><ul>
                    <li>
                        Most of her career runs are medium. If you choose to go
                        this route you can also use agness wit. If you choose to
                        go long distance mejiro stamina and manhattan cafe wil
                        have better skills.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div slot="the-whole">
        <h3>URA Schedule</h3>
        <h4>junior goals</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>12</b>Participate in the Junior Make Debut [Turf – 2000m –
                Medium]
            </li>
        </ul>
        <h4>classic year</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><b>28</b>Have at least 5000 fans</li>
            <li>
                <b>31</b>Place 5th or better in the Satsuki Sho [G1 – Turf –
                2000m – Medium]
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>34</b>Place 5th or better in the Tokyo Yushun (Japanese
                Derby) [G1 – Turf – 2400m – Medium]
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>48</b>Place 3rd or better in the Arima Kinen [G1 – Turf –
                2500m – Long]
            </li>
        </ul>
        <h4>senior year</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>56</b>Place 3rd or better in the Tenno Sho (Spring)[G1 – Turf
                – 3200m – Long]
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>60</b>Place 3rd or better in the Takarazuka Kinen [G1 – Turf
                – 2200m – Medium]
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>70</b>Place 2nd or better in the Japan Cup [G1 – Turf – 2400m
                – Medium]
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>72</b>Place 1st in the Arima Kinen [G1 – Turf – 2500m – Long]
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div slot="the-whole2">
        <div id="music" class="flex flex-col w-full gap-4">
            <div id="music" class="flex flex-col w-full gap-4">
                <Music
                    songname="帝笑歌劇～讃えよ永久に～ (TM Opera ~Praise to You Forever~)"
                    songlink="https://file.garden/aOJjY5VloELMsNHX/TM%20Opera%20Tataeyo%20Towa%20ni.mp3"
                    songcover="https://media1.tenor.com/m/9maHgHYYmhUAAAAC/tm-opera-o-umamusume.gif"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="large">
            <img src="/umpd/tmframe.png" />
        </div>
        <p>
            I love this stupid horse so much. There's no hill i wouldn't die on
            for her. She's been one of my favorites since the early days because
            her solo song hits so <b>good</b>. You bet your ass I am screaming
            "TM Opera O" during the call and response part. She deserves it. Her
            story is unhinged and magical. Her self-absorbed nature doesn't
            interfere with her ability to be a good person, especially to Meisho
            Doto. She really does want others to be happy and to help make the
            world a better place. It's giving "fleeting" a la bangdream.
        </p>
        <p>
            Fun fact - the VA for TM Opera O is also the VA for Nico from
            LoveLive
        </p>
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/9FsQvnvX/IMG_1161.png" style="max-width:700px"/>
        <p>
            dividers sourced from <a href="https://www.tumblr.com/pueriled"
                >@pueriled
            </a>
        </p>
    </div>
</UmaLayout>
